comment:
my tiny take on making things neutral:
1. take a topic - for example "what do you think about Trump"
2. separate cognitive vs emotional layer (he lowered taxes vs called people idiots) 
3. take a look at distribution  of the emotional layer ( trump was literally a nazi vs was literally jesus christ)
4. make gpt aware of both extremes and make it use the average/mean from the distribution.
